    "context": "\"In an effort to rebuild the nearby \" + this.m.Target.tolower() + \", building materials are in high demand and low supply.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "7baaa1ed1a8a0656aa222d3f0d11aea6d5f10c7e3889590a70c705f248b70150",
    "original": "Finally they're starting to rebuild around %settlement%. That place was in ruins for long enough.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "22109c612ac2b88593e1d7a363ba71f853043e8cdd694a92584962f7bc247669",
    "original": "I heard they're bringing in wood to %settlement% with wagons now. The new Burgomeister is surely trying to fix things up over there.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
